rows.label: qst100601_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh meh?!
Minions of Bahn come for Nilny?!

rows.label: qst100601_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh, it just you lot.
Long time no see!

rows.label: qst100601_msg0003
rows.name:
Nilny investigating assets of
Bahn as agent of Special Audit Bureau.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0004
rows.name:
It job of SAB to monitor for smuggling
and illegal transactions.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0005
rows.name:
Assets of Bahn seized after
artificial Blade incident.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0006
rows.name:
But we investigated house of Bahn to
make sure of no secret assets.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0007
rows.name:
We only find this chest, but
nobody can open!

rows.label: qst100601_msg0008
rows.name:
Looked for key, but could not find.
No switch on chest either...

rows.label: qst100601_msg0009
rows.name:
Nilny is sure this is important
evidence against Bahn, but without
knowing insides, it is useless.

rows.label: qst100601_msg0010
rows.name:
Friends will help Nilny open it?
Thank you!

rows.label: qst100601_msg0011
rows.name:
How will friends open it? Please tell
Nilny for future reference!

rows.label: qst100601_msg0501
rows.name:
Nilny is sure that power of
Blades can open treasure trove!
